Package: fono
Architecture: linux-any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Recommends: pipewire | pulseaudio, wtype | ydotool | xdotool
Description: Lightweight native voice dictation
 Fono is a single-binary Rust voice dictation tool: press a hotkey,
 speak, and cleaned text is typed at the cursor. Local Whisper + Qwen
 models by default, or bring-your-own cloud keys (Groq, OpenAI,
 Cerebras, Anthropic, ...). No Electron, no WebKit, no Python runtime.
